{"type": "article", "id": 27853, "title": "预报天气的智能雨伞", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-07T06:51:44Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 40, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702132801ei84PWDdSBR7tpXg.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>还是每天通过天气应用来确认要不要带伞出门？为什么不让伞自己告诉你呢？TARAbrella 是一把内置气象预报系统的智能雨伞，无需配套的手机应用。每 35 秒，内置的气压计就会检测一次大气气压，微处理器会把数据和湿度表检测到的湿度进行综合，对天气进行预测。根据天气情况，伞柄上的 LED 灯会显示不同的颜色。除此之外，它还配备了一个防盗配件，一旦它与你的距离超过 10 米，配件就会发出哔哔声提醒你。虽然有那么多的功能模块，这把智能雨伞本身却比 iPhone 还要轻，仅重 198 克。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/tarabrella-the-world-s-first-super-umbrella#/\">链接</a>参与众筹，最低价为 49 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132758RSyIFspxq9AP0fnc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132758cM6Kifz2aQOEbmDv.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68064516\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132759pgJQcqwnMulHeU3y.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}